    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a major project or a donor car for parts. The engine is currently non-operational and will require a full rebuild, and the transmission shows signs of significant wear. The body has noticeable rust in the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior requires a complete restoration due to heavy wear and tear. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
